rows.label: bf07450100_0020
rows.name:
Why are you running?
Why are you protecting this garbage?

rows.label: bf07450100_0030
rows.name: We Holy Grails don't need these things!

rows.label: bf07450100_0040
rows.name: You want to be free of them as I do!

rows.label: bf07450100_0050
rows.name:
Stop it!
I don't want that!

rows.label: bf07450100_0080
rows.name: Well damn, Father... Look what you've been hiding away.

rows.label: bf07450100_0090
rows.name:
All right, then.
If that's what you want, I'll do it for you!
